@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_xeeblp(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = (wp.sin(0.82) + wp.cos((v0 + 0.10 / v1 + 0.72)))
    v0 = tmp
    v2 = (wp.abs((tmp + 0.48 + tmp + 0.65)) * (wp.sin(v1 + 0.18) - (v2 + 0.67 - tmp + 0.31)))
    v0 = (wp.exp(wp.sin(v2 + 0.78)) / (v1 - wp.sin(tmp + 0.46)))
    v1 = 0.46
    data[tid] = v0
